spec file = test file to be executed
describe = test suite  = it block
single spec file has multiple describe
run command:  npx wdio run wdio.conf.js
Asserrtion in wdio is inbuilt
Locatorin wdio :
W dio support xpath, css and linked text as locators
 CSS: 
       // -- tagname[attribute=value]
       // #id
       // .classname
XPath:
   XPath: //tagname[@attribute='value']

Validatig the locating in console of dev tools:
  $("input[name='username']")  // wrap the locator and hit enter
  $x("//tagname[@attribute='value']")
  
Waitmechanism:
  method is waitUntill //  browser.waitUntil(condition, { timeout, timeoutMsg, interval })